The §6Enrichment Chamber§r is a machine that can be used to §eextract dust out of materials and ores§r (§7Not to be confused with the §6Crusher§r). You can make §eCompressed materials§r like §6Compressed Carbon§r, §6Compressed Redstone§r, §6Compressed Diamonds§r, etc.

To craft the chamber, you will need four §6Redstone Dust§r, two §6Iron Ingot§rs, two §6Basic Control Circuit§rs, and a §6Steel Casing§r.
